name: Roy Tang
text: Grabe nagvolunteer, ano ba namang rationalization  yan. All of them are sticking to the shootout story, walang nagsasabi na ayaw lang nila mapatay. Besides, Duterte himself makes no distinction as to which cops he's refering to basta lahat ng involved dun sa Espinosa death.
